<div type="definition">
<p>ARTEFACT RESEMBLING a FACE AND WORN ON the FACE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>ART 5.</p>
<p>方相，方形四目面具，多由領舞的巫師佩戴。</p>
<p>倛，兩目面具。</p>
<p>魌頭，死者所戴面具。</p>
<p>鋪，飾於門戶的獸形面具。</p>
        </div>
